                        <p>10.  Currito! Burritos without borders, indeed. If I hadn’t just spent $1,500 traveling to residency interviews, I’d open my own franchise.</p>
<p>Alex Fanaroff is a fourth-year medical student. His column runs every Wednesday.</p>

